 but <i>Hob</i> and <i>Dob</i>, which were common in the Middle Ages and gave rise to surnames, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]},{"name":"de","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["‘Attainment’."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Earl Robert de Menlan was born about 1109, in Normandy, France. He had at least 1 daughter with Maud de Dunstanville."},"et":{"about 1109–":"umbes 1109–Surnud","1143–1207":"1143–1207","1168–1204":"1168–1204","1109–Male":"1109–Surnud","about 1109":"umbes 1109","1204":"1204","1168":"1168","1143":"1143","about 1168":"umbes 1168","1109":"1109","1207":"1207","Meulan-en-Yvelines, Yvelines, Île-de-France, France":"Meulan-en-Yvelines, Yvelines, Île-de-France, Prantsusmaa","Normandy, France":"Normandie, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"about 1109–":"noin 1109–Kuollut","1143–1207":"1143–1207","1168–1204":"1168–1204","1109–Male":"1109–Kuollut","about 1109":"noin 1109","1204":"1204","1168":"1168","1143":"1143","about 1168":"noin 1168","1109":"1109","1207":"1207","Meulan-en-Yvelines, Yvelines, Île-de-France, France":"Meulan-en-Yvelines, Yvelines, Île-de-France, Ranska","Normandy, France":"Normandie, Ranska"},"fr":{"about 1109–":"environ 1109–Décédé","1143–1207":"1143–1207","1168–1204":"1168–1204","1109–Male":"1109–Décédé","about 1109":"environ 1109","1204":"1204","1168":"1168","1143":"1143","about 1168":"environ 1168","1109":"1109","1207":"1207","Meulan-en-Yvelines, Yvelines, Île-de-France, France":"Meulan-en-Yvelines, Yvelines, Île-de-France, France","Normandy, France":"Normandie, France","lifeSummary":"Earl Robert de Menlan est né environ 1109, à Normandie, France. Il a eu au moins 1 fille avec Maud de Dunstanville."},"de":{"about 1109–":"um 1109–Verstorben","1143–1207":"1143–1207","1168–1204":"1168–1204","1109–Male":"1109–Verstorben","about 1109":"um 1109","1204":"1204","1168":"1168","1143":"1143","about 1168":"um 1168","1109":"1109","1207":"1207","Meulan-en-Yveline